members.name: values
members.comment: Returns an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared.

return: an array containing the constants of this enum type, in the order they are declared

members.name: valueOf
members.comment: Returns the enum constant of this type with the specified name. The string must match exactly an identifier used to declare an enum constant in this type. (Extraneous whitespace characters are not permitted.)

param: name - the name of the enum constant to be returned.
throws: IllegalArgumentException - if this enum type has no constant with the specified name
NullPointerException - if the argument is null
return: the enum constant with the specified name

members.name: isKeyboardClick
members.comment: Gets whether this ClickType represents the pressing of a key on a keyboard.

return: true if this ClickType represents the pressing of a key

members.name: isCreativeAction
members.comment: Gets whether this ClickType represents an action that can only be performed by a Player in creative mode.

return: true if this action requires Creative mode

members.name: isRightClick
members.comment: Gets whether this ClickType represents a right click.

return: true if this ClickType represents a right click

members.name: isLeftClick
members.comment: Gets whether this ClickType represents a left click.

return: true if this ClickType represents a left click

members.name: isShiftClick
members.comment: Gets whether this ClickType indicates that the shift key was pressed down when the click was made.

return: true if the action uses Shift.
